# Date Picker

**Figma:** [Date Picker](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=128-10423&p=f&m=dev)

Input, popover, calendar, and selected date styling below are derived from Figma node 128:10423.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Input | Same as Text Input (ds-input.mdc) |
| Popover surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Popover border | `--border-base-default` |
| Selected date | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Today | `--border-brand-default` |

---

## Structure

### Input
- Same as Text Input; calendar icon.
- See ds-input.mdc for full specs.

### Popover
- **Surface:** `--bg-base-default`.
- **Border:** `--border-base-default`.
- **Shadow:** shadow-lg.

### Calendar
- **Selected date:** `--bg-brand-tertiary` background.
- **Today:** `--border-brand-default` border or outline.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10423.
